{% layout none %}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>I Switched My Wine for This on Tuesdays — Happie Fusion</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Sarah swapped her Tuesday wine for Happie. 6 weeks in, she just wants to feel like herself — slower. Use code SARAH15 for 15% off.">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500;1,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --cream:     #F5EFE3;
      --cream-lt:  #FAF6EC;
      --cream-dk:  #E8DFC9;
      --moss:      #5F7158;
      --moss-dk:   #3F4E3A;
      --moss-lt:   #8FA083;
      --warm:      #C9A84C;
      --warm-lt:   #E8D5A3;
      --cherry:    #B83A56;
      --cherry-lt: #D9637D;
      --brown:     #3D2F22;
      --brown-lt:  #6B5743;
      --paper:     #FDF9EF;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--brown);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    .serif { font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    .lp-nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      background: rgba(253,249,239,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(61,47,34,0.08);
    }
    .lp-nav-logo img { height: 44px; width: auto; display: block; }
    .lp-nav-cta {
      background: var(--moss-dk); color: var(--cream-lt);
      border-radius: 50px; padding: 9px 22px;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 130px 32px 70px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(165deg, #F5EFE3 0%, #EFE5D0 50%, #E5D8BC 100%);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px; align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-creator-tag {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(95,113,88,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(95,113,88,0.2);
      color: var(--moss-dk);
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-creator-tag-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--moss); animation: pulse 2.5s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.4; } }

    .hero-headline {
      font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 64px);
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.08;
      color: var(--brown); margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .hero-headline::before { content: '"'; color: var(--cherry); margin-right: 4px; }
    .hero-headline::after  { content: '"'; color: var(--cherry); margin-left: 4px; }

    .hero-attribution {
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--brown-lt);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 32px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    }
    .hero-attribution-avatar {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cherry), var(--moss));
      color: var(--cream-lt);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
    }
    .hero-attribution-handle { color: var(--moss-dk); font-weight: 600; }

    .hero-body {
      font-size: 17px; color: var(--brown-lt);
      line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 36px;
      max-width: 460px;
    }
    .hero-body strong { color: var(--brown); }

    .hero-cta-group {
      display: inline-flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      background: var(--moss-dk); color: var(--cream-lt);
      border-radius: 50px; padding: 17px 36px;
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(63,78,58,0.25);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--moss); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .hero-code-display {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      background: rgba(184,58,86,0.08);
      border: 1.5px dashed var(--cherry);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 10px 18px;
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--brown);
    }
    .hero-code-display strong {
      font-family: 'Inter', monospace;
      background: var(--cherry); color: var(--cream-lt);
      padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-weight: 800;
    }

    /* Hero visual */
    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
      display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
      min-height: 480px;
    }
    .hero-can-wrap {
      position: relative;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 32px 60px rgba(184,58,86,0.25));
    }
    .hero-can-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(201,168,76,0.4) 0%, transparent 70%);
      transform: scale(1.5);
    }
    .hero-can {
      width: 280px; max-width: 80vw; position: relative;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }
    .hero-quote-card {
      position: absolute; top: 30px; right: -10px;
      background: var(--cream-lt);
      border: 1px solid rgba(61,47,34,0.1);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      max-width: 200px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(61,47,34,0.12);
      transform: rotate(2deg);
    }
    .hero-quote-card-text {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 13px; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brown); line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .hero-quote-card-by {
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--moss-dk);
      font-weight: 700; margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .hero-flavor-tag {
      position: absolute; bottom: 20px; left: -20px;
      background: var(--cherry);
      color: var(--cream-lt);
      border-radius: 50px; padding: 8px 18px;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      transform: rotate(-3deg);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(184,58,86,0.3);
    }

    /* ── 6 WEEKS LATER ── */
    .ritual-section {
      padding: 100px 32px;
      background: var(--cream-lt);
    }
    .ritual-inner { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .ritual-eyebrow {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cherry);
      margin-bottom: 18px; text-align: center;
    }
    .ritual-headline {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
      font-weight: 500; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brown); line-height: 1.2;
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .ritual-quote {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px);
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--brown-lt); line-height: 1.55;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 32px;
      background: var(--paper);
      border-radius: 24px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--cherry);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .ritual-quote::before {
      content: '"'; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 30px;
      font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 80px;
      color: rgba(184,58,86,0.15); line-height: 1;
    }
    .ritual-author {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--moss-dk); font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── COMPARE ── */
    .compare-section {
      padding: 100px 32px;
      background: var(--paper);
    }
    .compare-inner {
      max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .compare-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .compare-eyebrow {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--moss);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .compare-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
      font-weight: 600; color: var(--brown);
      line-height: 1.15;
    }
    .compare-title em { color: var(--cherry); font-style: italic; }
    .compare-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px;
    }
    .compare-col {
      background: var(--cream-lt);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 36px 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61,47,34,0.06);
    }
    .compare-col.cherry {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #FBEFED, #F2DDD9);
      border-color: rgba(184,58,86,0.15);
    }
    .compare-col-label {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .compare-col.wine .compare-col-label { background: rgba(61,47,34,0.1); color: var(--brown); }
    .compare-col.cherry .compare-col-label { background: var(--cherry); color: var(--cream-lt); }
    .compare-col h3 {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--brown); margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .compare-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .compare-list li {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--brown-lt);
      line-height: 1.7; padding: 8px 0;
    }
    .compare-list li svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ── INGREDIENT ── */
    .ingredient-section {
      padding: 100px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--paper) 0%, var(--cream) 100%);
    }
    .ingredient-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px; align-items: center;
    }
    .ingredient-text h2 {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
      font-weight: 600; color: var(--brown);
      line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .ingredient-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--cherry); }
    .ingredient-text p {
      font-size: 16px; color: var(--brown-lt);
      line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .ingredient-stack {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }
    .ingredient-card {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px;
      background: var(--cream-lt);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61,47,34,0.07);
    }
    .ingredient-card-dose {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--moss-dk); min-width: 70px;
    }
    .ingredient-card-info strong {
      display: block; font-size: 14px; color: var(--brown);
      font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .ingredient-card-info span {
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--brown-lt); line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .ingredient-visual {
      position: relative;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(201,168,76,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 32px;
      padding: 48px; text-align: center;
    }
    .ingredient-num {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 100px; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--cherry); line-height: 1;
    }
    .ingredient-num-suffix {
      font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--brown-lt); text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700; margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .ingredient-divider {
      width: 60px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--cherry);
      margin: 20px auto;
    }
    .ingredient-blurb {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 15px; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brown-lt); line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 280px; margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── REVIEWS ── */
    .reviews-section {
      padding: 100px 32px;
      background: var(--cream);
    }
    .reviews-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .reviews-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .reviews-eyebrow {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cherry);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .reviews-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 600; color: var(--brown);
    }
    .reviews-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px;
    }
    .review-card {
      background: var(--paper);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 28px 26px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61,47,34,0.06);
    }
    .review-stars {
      color: var(--warm); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .review-text {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 15px; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brown-lt); line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .review-by {
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--moss-dk);
      font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── TRUST BAR ── */
    .trust-section {
      padding: 60px 32px;
      background: var(--moss-dk);
      color: var(--cream-lt);
    }
    .trust-inner {
      max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .trust-item { padding: 0 16px; }
    .trust-item + .trust-item { border-left: 1px solid rgba(245,239,227,0.15); }
    .trust-item svg { stroke: var(--warm-lt); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .trust-item strong { display: block; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 800; }
    .trust-item span { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(245,239,227,0.65); }

    /* ── FINAL CTA ── */
    .final-cta {
      padding: 130px 32px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 70%, rgba(184,58,86,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(165deg, var(--cream) 0%, var(--cream-dk) 100%);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .final-cta-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .final-cta h2 {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 500; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brown); line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .final-cta h2 em { color: var(--cherry); }
    .final-cta p {
      font-size: 17px; color: var(--brown-lt);
      line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
    }
    .final-cta-code-row {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center;
    }
    .disclaimer {
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--brown-lt); opacity: 0.6;
      max-width: 540px; margin: 40px auto 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    .lp-footer {
      padding: 28px 32px;
      background: var(--brown);
      color: rgba(245,239,227,0.7);
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .lp-footer-links { display: flex; gap: 22px; }
    .lp-footer-links a:hover { color: var(--cream-lt); }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-inner, .ingredient-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 56px; }
      .hero { padding: 110px 24px 60px; }
      .hero-visual { order: -1; min-height: 380px; }
      .hero-can { width: 220px; }
      .hero-quote-card { right: -10px; top: 10px; max-width: 170px; }
      .compare-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
      .trust-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 24px; }
      .trust-item + .trust-item { border-left: none; }
      .trust-item:nth-child(odd) { border-right: 1px solid rgba(245,239,227,0.15); }
      .lp-footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; text-align: center; }
      section { padding-left: 20px !important; padding-right: 20px !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="lp-nav">
    <a href="/" class="lp-nav-logo"><img src="{{ 'happie-logo.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Happie Fusion"></a>
    <a href="/collections/all?discount=SARAH15" class="lp-nav-cta">Use SARAH15 →</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="hero-creator-tag">
          <span class="hero-creator-tag-dot"></span>
          Creator Recommended
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-headline serif">I switched my wine for this on Tuesdays</h1>
        <div class="hero-attribution">
          <div class="hero-attribution-avatar">S</div>
          <span>— <span class="hero-attribution-handle">@sarah_handle</span> · Wellness Creator</span>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-body">Six weeks ago, Sarah swapped her Tuesday-night Cabernet for a can of Happie. Her words: <strong>"I don't want to feel anything wild. I want to feel like me, slower."</strong></p>
        <div class="hero-cta-group">
          <a href="/collections/all?discount=SARAH15" class="btn-primary">
            Try Sarah's Ritual →
          </a>
          <div class="hero-code-display">
            Use code <strong>SARAH15</strong> for 15% off your first order
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="hero-can-wrap">
          <div class="hero-can-bg"></div>
          <img src="{{ 'can-blue-razzberry.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Happie Fungi Fusion can" class="hero-can">
          <div class="hero-quote-card">
            <div class="hero-quote-card-text">"Feels like the part of wine I actually liked. None of the part I didn't."</div>
            <div class="hero-quote-card-by">— Week 3, Sarah's notes</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-flavor-tag">Cheery Cherry</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6 WEEKS LATER -->
  <section class="ritual-section">
    <div class="ritual-inner">
      <div class="ritual-eyebrow">Six Weeks Later</div>
      <h2 class="ritual-headline">She just wanted to feel like herself — <em>slower.</em></h2>
      <div class="ritual-quote">
        I didn't want to quit drinking. I just didn't want to lose my Tuesdays anymore. Wednesdays were starting to suffer. I tried Happie because a friend sent me one, and I kept reaching for it. Six weeks in, I sleep better. I read more. I'm not anti-wine — I'm pro feeling like myself.
      </div>
      <div class="ritual-author">— @sarah_handle, six weeks in</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMPARE: WINE vs HAPPIE -->
  <section class="compare-section">
    <div class="compare-inner">
      <div class="compare-header">
        <div class="compare-eyebrow">A Quieter Tuesday</div>
        <h2 class="compare-title serif">The same ritual.<br><em>Without the next-day cost.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="compare-grid">
        <div class="compare-col wine">
          <div class="compare-col-label">Tuesday Wine</div>
          <h3 class="serif">What you give up</h3>
          <ul class="compare-list">
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
              Slower Wednesday morning
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
              Interrupted sleep cycles
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
              That low-grade anxiety the next day
